dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents Literary Arts Non-profits for New Orleans, LA in 2018. The file represents cultural assets in the City of New Orleans related to groups that meet or discuss readings and creative writings, in order to continue interest in and knowledge of literature for current and future generations. This file was downloaded on December, 2018 by NYU Data Services. It was originally represented on the New Orleans Open Data Socrata portal as catalog record ggns-r5yf
dc_title_s: Literary Arts Non-profits for New Orleans, LA, 2018
